Package: bmiheatr
Title: Basic Model Interface Example in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mark", "Piper", email = "mark.piper@colorado.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Stefan", "Verhoeven", email = "s.verhoeven@esciencecenter.nl", role = "aut"),
    person("Community Surface Dynamics Modeling System", role = "cph"))
Description:
    An example implementation of the Basic Model Interface (BMI) in R.
    This package provides a simple heat diffusion model that is wrapped with
    a BMI using the BMI R mappings.
URL: https://bmi.csdms.io, https://csdms.colorado.edu
